# 🖼️ Image Gallery Project

## 📌 Project Description
This project is a responsive Image Gallery built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.  
It displays images in a clean grid layout with interactive features like hover effects, lightbox view, and navigation buttons.

---

## 🚀 Features
- Responsive image grid layout
- Hover effects with smooth transitions
- Lightbox view for enlarged images
- Next and Previous navigation buttons
- Mobile-friendly responsive design

---

## 🎁 Bonus Features
- Image filter by category
- Smooth animation effects

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript

